Hamilton Lane Looks at 25 Companies to Co-Invest, Chairman Says

-- B y   F r a n c i s c o   M a r c e l i n o
-- 
2011-12-06T20:36:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/hamilton-lane-looks-at-25-companies-to-co-invest-chairman-says.html
Hamilton Lane Advisors LLC, the
private-equity fund partly owned by  Bill Gates , is looking at
about 25 companies to co-invest, Chairman Hartley Rogers said.  Hamilton Lane, based in  Bala Cynwyd ,  Pennsylvania , sees a
“very good pipeline right now,” Hartley said in an interview
in  Sao Paulo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francisco Marcelino in Sao Paulo at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scheer at   dscheer@bloomberg.net  